OL,3,CDad found guilty of 'horrifically'
OL,4,Cmurdering two-year-old son
OL,6,FA dad who "horrifically" killed his
OL,7,Ftwo-year-old son within weeks of being
OL,8,Fgranted full-time care of the little
OL,9,Fboy has been found guilty of his
OL,10,Fmurder.
OL,12,FDaniel Hardcastle, 31, watched a
OL,13,FYouTube video on how to perform CPR
OL,14,Fbefore calling paramedics to treat his
OL,15,Fson, Damion Russell, who died after
OL,16,Fsuffering a traumatic head injury.
OL,18,FThe tattoo artist had taken on care of
OL,19,Fthe boy after learning he was a
OL,20,Ffather, and moved to a flat in Central
OL,21,FDrive, Blackpool, in July 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
