OL,3,CDad found guilty of 'horrifically'
OL,4,Cmurdering two-year-old son
OL,6,FJust three months later on 19 August
OL,7,F2023 at 11:09am, Hardcastle rang 999
OL,8,Fsaying his son was unresponsive and
OL,9,Finjured after "running into a coffee
OL,10,Ftable".
OL,12,FDamion was taken to Blackpool Victoria
OL,13,FHospital and later transferred to
OL,14,FManchester Children's Hospital where
OL,15,Fmedics fought to save his life, but he
OL,16,Fdied four days later.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
