OL,3,CDad found guilty of 'horrifically'
OL,4,Cmurdering two-year-old son
OL,6,FTests concluded he had suffered
OL,7,Frespiratory arrest, followed by
OL,8,Fcardiac arrest, "most likely caused
OL,9,Ffrom forceful shaking in combination
OL,10,Fwith a head impact".
OL,12,FThe toddler had also been bitten on
OL,13,Fhis right thigh, had a rib fracture,
OL,14,Fdamage to his upper lip and extensive
OL,15,Fbruising to the whole of his body.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
