OL,3,CDad found guilty of 'horrifically'
OL,4,Cmurdering two-year-old son
OL,6,FBut following a lengthy trial at
OL,7,FPreston Crown Court, Hardcastle was
OL,8,Ffound guilty of murder.
OL,10,FTom Snape, Senior Crown Prosecutor for
OL,11,FCPS North West said: "Damion's life
OL,12,Fhas been cruelly cut short by his own
OL,13,Ffather, Daniel Hardcastle.
OL,15,F"As his father, Hardcastle should have
OL,16,Fcared for him and protected him from
OL,17,Fharm. Instead, he assaulted Damion so
OL,18,Fviolently and with such force that it
OL,19,Fcaused extensive injuries which led to
OL,20,Fhis death."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
